	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>Pointing at a creature you can see, you call upon dark forces, shooting a beam of necrotic energy that rots or weathers your target. If your target is undead, you are temporarily magically bound together by dark tendrils.</em></p><p><strong>Ranged Spell Attack</strong> </p><ul><li><p><strong>Hit:</strong> Target takes [[/damage 1d8 necrotic]] damage<strong>*</strong> and target cannot be healed. If target is undead, target has disadvantage on attack rolls.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>*At Higher Levels:</strong> This spell's damage increases by 1d8 when you reach a total character or creature level of 5th level ([[/damage 2d8 necrotic]]), 11th level ([[/damage 3d8 necrotic]]), and 17th level ([[/damage 4d8 necrotic]]).</p><p><em>Negative energy refers to dark magic that drains life or rots and weathers whatever it touches. Whether an elf, a zombie, or a wooden door, most things are susceptible.</em></p>",
			"chat": ""
		},
